This is not a one-off clip. This is a DECADES LONG documented pattern captured by C-SPAN, AP, Reuters and White House pool photographers across multiple administrations. Nikki Haley. Brigitte Macron. Female Secret Service agents. The gesture is consistent. The gender is consistent. The power dynamic is consistent. ??

In the United States Secret Service, physical contact with protectees is strictly minimized and protocol driven. Uninvited touch is discouraged and reported. The President of the United States is routinely touching female agents in ways that would get anyone else pulled from their detail. Nobody says anything. ?️?

It's not one video. It's not a partisan clip. It's a fucking pattern documented across thirty years of public footage. Patterns reveal intent. The pattern here is very clear and has been visible to anyone paying attention since approximately 1987. ???? 

#TrumpPattern #SecretService #PowerDynamics #GenderedConduct #DocumentedPattern #NotOneClip #ThirtyYears #ProtocolViolation #BodyLanguage #PatternsRevealIntent</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/C1oJ22C</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JamieGeorge]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>KPDH Mini-Dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QzIEebo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cbKegb6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f8jD7kK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3h9oZht.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GEvUpVL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OcseGvv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qYEMuhE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2r3L4Nv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9hZL45V.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bED0ASf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Audrey Nuna, EJAE, and Rei Ami - singing voices</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/idjv9NT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>May Hong, Ji-Young Yoo, and Arden Cho - speaking voices</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Narrbob.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Posting in honor of their Oscar wins and the sequel announcement. I’m such a huge fan. I’ve rewatched it like 7 times (would be more