There is no danger to your kittens, they are kicking up a storm and you are eating and pooping and playing and showing no signs of distress, so that’s not what this is about. I’m just tired. And I know you are, too. 

I’m just not used to waiting this long. Every other pregnant mama cat I have fostered has popped within DAYS. I know that just means I got you much earlier in your pregnancy, but it’s still hard to wait.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zTNSd7E.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Guatemala trips and fostering kittens are the most important parts of my life and I was happy to skip the trip to be here with you, but I also left my team at work hanging by taking off this week. I’m gonna walk into a shitstorm Monday. Not looking forward to that. 

I’m infinitely glad that I was able to bond with you and stuff your face with all the best, most nutrient-rich food and let your dog-bite wounds heal because all of that is ultimately the best for you and your kittens. I’m not discounting that. But…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QiufjVE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>…I was just hoping to have a few days to hang out with you and your babies - AFTER they’ve been born - to make sure they’re all healthy and growing and you don’t have any nursing issues. Anyways, thanks for listening to me, Bobbie. I will, of course, wait as long as you need me to. But I am locked and loaded and ready to go!! 

I’ve decided I’m gonna stop obsessively staring at your belly and holding my breath and hoping…it’s fraying my nerves. I’m just gonna try to enjoy these last two days I have off work, spend time with you, watch Scandal, and put all of this in your capable paws. I trust you. ::sigh::</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6Xbtv8w</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KittensForDays]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tensions between the US and Japan over Iran were clear Thursday as President Trump asked Japan's Prime Minister Sanae Takaichi, "Why didn't you tell me about Pearl Harbor?" – Takaichi didn't laugh and instead pursed her lips and glanced at her advisers</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xSIZXhK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TBtnki5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The latest instance of a foreign leader being put on the back foot in a White House meeting, with [Huff and Puff] Trump trying to bully/leverage them to extract concessions or criticize their policies as counter to US [His] interests.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xSIZXhK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OceansRust]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Disney animation in the past</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/z7rWnZq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UJRcqR2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/z7rWnZq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DOcelot1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Israel never wanted peace - only chaos</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vUzzXGD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wQ94CY3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vUzzXGD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[chukyrlaw]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I was unprepared for this</tit